{
  "texts": [
    "Data acquisition.",
    "The data acquisition methods in this paper include three parts.",
    "The first one is manual synthesis, where realistic synthesis operations are performed by using Photoshop (PS) on the collected railroad scenes.",
    "The second is an automatic generation method based on ChatGPT and AIGC.",
    "The third is data synthesis based on the Railsem19 28 dataset."
  ]
}